YOSEMITE HOSPITALITY, LLC  Trademark Information
 Yosemite Hospitality, LLC
Clothing, namely, T-shirts, shirts, ties, sweat shirts, jackets, shorts, pants, hats, visors, caps, gloves, sweaters, coats, scarves, skirts, aprons, suspenders, belts, underwear and socks
Retail store services featuring gasoline; retail store services featuring food, beverages, souvenirs and novelty items; online retail store services featuring souvenirs and novelty items; concession stands featuring food, beverages, souvenirs and novelty items; food kiosk services; vending in the field of beverages, snacks and food; mobile kiosk services
Organization of and conducting sightseeing travel tours for others; conducting sightseeing travel tours by airplane, bicycle, bus, car, mule and horse; rental of bikes; rental of mules and horses for transportation purposes
Recreational services in the nature of downhill skiing, cross-country skiing, hiking, ice skating, horse-back riding, mule riding, tennis; education services, namely, providing instruction in the field of mountaineering and providing mountaineering guide services; educational and entertainment services, namely, providing lectures and cooking demonstrations in the culinary arts; educational and entertainment services, namely, providing educatio...
Hotel, restaurant and bar services; cafeteria services; contract food, refreshment and beverage services; catering services; coffee shops




