 Mark Description: 
The mark consists of the word "YOSEMITE" in dark green above the words "HOSPITALITY, LLC" in dark green with two dark green dots on each side above three white trees with a white line going through inside a half filled light green circle with light green outline of mountains at the top of circle, with the top mountain portion in white color.


