Merced River Whitewater Rafting
Apr-Jul, starting at $122 adult; $111 child 10 to 17 years


Enjoy a full or half day on one of California's best whitewater rafting paddle-boat trips. The 11-14 miles of rafting on the Merced is typically class 3 (rated 1-5, with 5 being most challenging), with a combination of memorable rapids and peaceful floats through pristine waters and scenic canyons.  This trip is suitable for first time rafters, and depending on water levels, children over age 7.
